posting_body: ['3rd, Top Floor 2BR/2BA', '* $2,725/month annual lease', '* Shared laundry', '* Shared deck', '* Elevator in building', "* Parking at an add'l fee", '*', 'Available:', 'Now', 'OPEN HOUSE: Tuesday(8/2) 7:45pm-8pm', 'Address: 301 Jayne #15', "Bright, contemporary, third, top floor 2BR/2BA apartment in Oakland's Adams Point.", 'Floors are hardwood except in bath.', 'Heat is via gas wall heater and floor radiators.', 'Open living room has kitchen in an alcove to one side of the entrance, windows at the opposite end, and one bedroom to each side.', 'Kitchen includes gas stove, dishwasher and microwave.', 'Both bedrooms have wall closets with sliding mirror doors and a private bath with shower-over-tub and sliding glass doors.', 'Building is on a quiet, two-block street just north of Lake Merritt.', 'Each floor has a shared deck overlooking the front of the building.', 'Building has an elevator and parking may be available for an additional fee.', 'The Walk Score is 85.', 'Shopping and dining on Grand Avenue are about five blocks away.', 'Transit Score is 64.', "Tenant pays a one-time broker's fee.", 'Everest Mwamba', 'DRE# 01717299', 'Kenney & Everest Real Estate', 'DRE# 01984640', 'show contact info', 'office', 'Apply at KenneyandEverest .', 'com', 'Leasing and Real Estate: Our Family Business for Over 100 Years.']
